Class FailedTestsToPass

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.zamia.BasicTest

  • public class FailedTestsToPass
extends BasicTest
    These tests must succeed but fail, unfortunately. I have grouped the tests but HierarchicalContextRunner support is still not perfect in Eclipse http://github.com/bechte/junit-hierarchicalcontextrunner/issues/6#issuecomment-32127032 You can run only all tests at once and to re-run, you must Run/Debug a @Test method in the top class.
